<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="bn">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
    <title>আমাদের সম্পর্কে | ODDHAY</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lexend:wght@300..900&family=Noto+Sans+Bengali:wght@300..900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: { "primary": "#137fec", "background-light": "#f6f7f8", "background-dark": "#101922" },
                    fontFamily: { "display": ["Lexend", "Noto Sans Bengali", "sans-serif"] },
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Lexend', 'Noto Sans Bengali', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-[#0d141b] dark:text-slate-100 min-h-screen">
    <header
        class="sticky top-0 z-[100] w-full border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white/90 dark:bg-background-dark/90 backdrop-blur-md px-6 py-4">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="text-primary"><svg class="size-8" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 48 48"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M4 4H17.3334V17.3334H30.6666V30.6666H44V44H4V4Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                    </svg></div>
                <h1 class="text-xl font-bold">ODDHAY</h1>
            </a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-bold opacity-80">
                <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">হোম</a>
                <a href="/courses" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">কোর্সসমূহ</a>
                <a href="/#features" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">সেবাসমূহ</a>
                <a href="/about" class="text-primary transition-colors">আমাদের সম্পর্কে</a>
                <a href="/#contact" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">যোগাযোগ</a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="hidden md:flex gap-3">
                    <% if (locals.user) { %>
                        <a href="/dashboard"
                            class="text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 text-primary hover:bg-primary/10 rounded-lg transition-all">ড্যাশবোর্ড</a>
                        <a href="/logout"
                            class="bg-red-500 text-white text-sm font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-md">লগআউট</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <a href="/login"
                                class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all text-sm">লগইন</a>
                            <a href="/register"
                                class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-primary text-white font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 hover:scale-105 transition-all text-sm">রেজিস্ট্রেশন</a>
                            <% } %>
                </div>
                <button class="p-2 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300"
                    onclick="document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark')">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined block dark:hidden">dark_mode</span>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined hidden dark:block">light_mode</span>
                </button>
                <button class="md:hidden p-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="menu-icon">menu</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile Menu Overlay -->
        <div id="mobile-menu"
            class="hidden fixed inset-0 z-[110] bg-white dark:bg-background-dark p-6 transition-transform duration-300 translate-x-full overflow-y-auto">
            <div class="flex justify-end mb-8">
                <button class="p-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300"
                    onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">close</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <nav class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center">
                <a class="text-2xl font-black hover:text-primary" href="/" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">হোম</a>
                <a class="text-2xl font-black hover:text-primary" href="/courses"
                    onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">কোর্সসমূহ</a>
                <a class="text-2xl font-black hover:text-primary" href="/#features"
                    onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">সেবাসমূহ</a>
                <a class="text-2xl font-black text-primary" href="/about" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">আমাদের
                    সম্পর্কে</a>
                <a class="text-2xl font-black hover:text-primary" href="/#contact"
                    onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">যোগাযোগ</a>
                <hr class="border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 my-4">
                <% if (locals.user) { %>
                    <a href="/dashboard"
                        class="py-3 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-xl font-bold text-xl">ড্যাশবোর্ড</a>
                    <a href="/logout" class="py-3 bg-red-500/10 text-red-500 rounded-xl font-bold text-xl">লগআউট</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/login"
                            class="py-4 border-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">লগইন
                            করুন</a>
                        <a href="/register"
                            class="py-4 bg-primary text-white rounded-2xl font-black text-xl shadow-xl shadow-primary/20">রেজিস্ট্রেশন
                            করুন</a>
                        <% } %>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <script>
        function toggleMobileMenu() {
            const menu = document.getElementById('mobile-menu');
            if (menu.classList.contains('hidden')) {
                menu.classList.remove('hidden');
                setTimeout(() => menu.classList.remove('translate-x-full'), 10);
            } else {
                menu.classList.add('translate-x-full');
                setTimeout(() => menu.classList.add('hidden'), 300);
            }
        }
    </script>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6">শিখুন আগামীর জন্য</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">ODDHAY হলো একটি আধুনিক এডটেক প্ল্যাটফর্ম, যা বাংলাদেশের
                মাধ্যমিক ও উচ্চ-মাধ্যমিক শিক্ষার্থীদের জন্য মানসম্মত শিক্ষা নিশ্চিত করতে প্রতিশ্রুতিবদ্ধ।</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
            <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-primary/10 aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text- primary text-9xl opacity-20">school</span>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black">আমাদের লক্ষ্য (Our Mission)</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">আমরা বিশ্বাস করি প্রতিটি শিক্ষার্থীর নিজস্ব মেধা আছে।
                    আমাদের লক্ষ্য হলো এআই এবং আধুনিক প্রযুক্তির ব্যবহারের মাধ্যমে সেই মেধাকে সঠিক পথে পরিচালিত করা। আমরা
                    পড়াশোনাকে শুধু ক্লাসরুমের গণ্ডিতে আটকে না রেখে তাকে আরও আনন্দদায়ক এবং কার্যকর করতে চাই।</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">১০k+</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">সক্রিয় শিক্ষার্থী</p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">৫০+</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">বিশেষজ্ঞ শিক্ষক</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer
        class="bg-white dark:bg-background-dark border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 py-10 text-center text-slate-500 text-sm">
        <p>© 2024 ODDHAY. অল রাইটস রিজার্ভড।</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>